staging: lustre: ptlrpc: add OBD_CONNECT_UNLINK_CLOSE flag

Add OBD_CONNECT_UNLINK_CLOSE flag for interop, once this is supported,
client packs file handle in unlink RPC, and MDT will close file before
unlink.

